12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: =
10pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 9pt; =
font-family: Helvetica;">On 2 September 2025, Tower confirmed the =
remaining amount under my temporary accommodation benefit was =
$13,820.62. As at 6 November 2025 (20 business days since my =
submission), I have received no acknowledgement, no payment, and no =
progress update, despite repeated follow-ups. While previous refunds of =
the same were acknowledged within about 3 business days and paid =
promptly.</span><span lang=3D"EN-NZ" style=3D"font-size: =
12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: =
