style=3D"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Helvetica;">In line with my policy =
commitment to prompt payment and the Fair Insurance Code obligations for =
timely communication, please:</span><span lang=3D"EN-NZ" =
style=3D"font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></div><ol start=3D"1" =
type=3D"1" style=3D"margin-bottom: 0in;"><li class=3D"MsoNormal" =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 9pt; font-family: =
Helvetica;">Process immediate payment of the temporary accommodation =
expenses submitted on 9 October 2025; and</span><span lang=3D"EN-NZ" =
style=3D"font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 9pt; font-family: =
Helvetica;">Confirm the payment date<span =
